Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海日誌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}6月9日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴風號全體船員 從前所未有的航海實習當中平安生還
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那件事已經過去了一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這期間 橫須賀女子海洋學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「藍色人魚」以及國土安全委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正在分析生命體「RATt」帶來的這齣意外的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並處理相關事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了預防疫情可能再次爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由海洋醫大建立的特殊隊伍正在研究對策
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這時的晴風號船員結束了期中考察
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即將進入考後假期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無仁義旁白風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寫航海日誌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.70,0:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是在陸地上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算在陸地上也要寫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊 今晚也一起看無仁義之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉打擾你們說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}午休結束以後來一下會議室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 提亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是要重新討論第二學期的課程表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為上次那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去晴風班的學生不能參與航海實習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因此 學校打算採取一些對策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的班級會被拆解？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長剛才才叫我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道就是這件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要老是往不好的地方想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且這次的事件都是靠晴風號的船員齊心協力才能解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該不會那麼輕易地拆班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也…也對
Comment: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:38.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}静かに燃える世界　始まりはここから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:59.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夜空が終わりを告げるとき
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:04.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ひとすじの光が　胸に秘めた声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}解き放つ　闇を裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:13.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}枯れるよりいっそ　散り急ぐ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:19.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷い　歩く術を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:26.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}千の波に　呑まれた心じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君さえ守れない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:34.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　鳴り止まぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:39.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}忘れられぬ傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今もかすかな残像　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:49.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界が待ってる　明日の産声を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:54.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}響け　確かな衝動　消えないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:04:02.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう未来と過去が交差する　百年目の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:54.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一切都始於這靜靜燃燒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:59.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在長夜將明之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:04.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一道光芒 一聲發自靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}衝破束縛 撕裂黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:13.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}尋求著歸宿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:19.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷茫地邁足前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:26.23,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}這顆被波濤掩去的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}甚至沒辦法保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:34.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 就像要跳出來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:39.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}留下無法忘卻的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:44.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}希望這微弱的殘影 永遠不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:49.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}世界正在等待 屬於明日的嬰啼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:54.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}心臟在胸中激盪 千萬不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:04:02.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}是的 這是一首交錯著過去與未來的百年長歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}越來越不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 航海的時候你那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須寫檢討書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我真的很討厭寫文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明 我把我的寫完就幫你 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 香香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知名艦長 別太寵我們的艦長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是稍微幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你叫我來難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能把這個交給班上的同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發給所有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}校長發給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說這很重要 一定要發給每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 我和艦長現在抽不出身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能麻煩你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 這是艦長的命令和摯友小白的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是你摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答應了就好 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘記問他們重新分班的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:50.17,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康特粗楷體\bord0\1c&H0E0F13&\fs30\frx348\fry354\frz14.65\move(380,262,474,494,0,1875)}6月13日　9:00前禁止啟封
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}密封命令書？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 晴風號的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次你們的使命是找出潛入橫須賀女子海洋學校的間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}願你們順利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這任務真是太難了 簡直就是碟中諜大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}八木同學 宇田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校的命令書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啟封時間已經指定了 千萬不要提前打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要把這些都發完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 艦長和副艦長都忙著整理文件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長她們真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這幾天明明休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 我們幫你發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是橫須賀人 正打算帶著小慧逛逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 反正順路 乾脆一邊發命令書一邊散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…你們原本也有安排的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都是同學 別那麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和小幸你在海上的時候沒什麼機會聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天和你好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宇田同學 八木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那事不宜遲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.05,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&H656361&\2aFF\frz26.86\pos(340,612)\frx354\fry358}學校有東西要交給大家，等一下我和納沙同學還\N有小慧一起去發，你{\k25}們{\k25}現{\k25}在{\k25}都{\k25}在{\k25}哪{\k25}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問 要開始做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我傳簡訊給全班同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要她們說一下自己在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是報務員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們應該很快就會回覆 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你缺了一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我數數…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的啊 只有12張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留奈果然缺牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不是配牌時忘記拿了一張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留奈你老是丟三落四的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於能立直囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明和不了你亂碰什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}1000 2000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斷么自摸 寶牌1…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真難打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人家好不容易立直了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓只會斷么的麗緒和倒無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你那牌和了我還怎麼打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來已經被看穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.39,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}犯規的應該被懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我又吊車尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是記錄員閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗緒 謝謝你回信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 畢竟注意到簡訊的也只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有東西要交給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是學校發的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼呢 是成績單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是規定了啟封時間的密封命令書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在啟封的話 就會因為違反校規停學的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你仔細看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好你沒有打開 留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.63,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來寫著禁止啟封啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小侖小黑不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機長她們幾個今天去研修了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}研修？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們是被選召的工程師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你們順利通過特別訓練 接受超一流的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種訓練 閉著眼都能過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就以超一流為目標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會是去做這樣的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我們的輪機長本領高超是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小黑也和輪機長很有默契
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雙強合璧無人能敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}命令書就交給我保管吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正也和輪機長約好了一起吃晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你聽說那個傳聞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傳聞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼傳聞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小橘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放假以後我也沒事做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以來這裡學做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我們家親戚開的店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且還有打工工資呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好和麗緒她們在一棟房子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 13號才能打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長她們好像很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直窩在圖書室裡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛剛我還送點心去慰勞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 關於這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我試做了一下 嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以嗎 那我不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在法式泡芙裡加了甜納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小茜 你太激進了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得這搭配不算差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小慧她討厭吃甜納豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還好吧 宇田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還行吧 我們繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其他人還沒回覆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道有個人肯定在那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 只有溫泉能洗去考試的疲勞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 能感受到愉快的電波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有的沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知踏上陸地也這麼英姿颯爽 酷斃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.46,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}零件這麼多 好難好難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.93,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帥啊 真知知好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畫得好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要畫出拿真知知做主角的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後拿去夏季大展上開賣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我猜野間同學可能會跑到很高的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還順便找到了另外三個人 運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸的推理真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴風號會被怎麼處置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是不是再也不能乘坐它了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪機長和黑木同學在研修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}後勤科的三個人在和式點心店學習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼偏偏在考完放假的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼一說 是有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二學期還有航海實習 但我們卻沒有能上的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果她們那麼做還有些別的打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然早就覺得她是位大小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但沒想到居然這麼有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大小姐 您應該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我馬上就回去 再給我一點時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 我會轉告的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你們躲在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有…有東西要交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勞煩你們特地跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…萬里小路同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛剛你們說的「回去」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實父親已經說好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 我要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的棋子要被拿下囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 又能拿一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小玉的夥伴們越來越少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}水上船塢都開過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是要撈上來拆掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟也不能一直丟在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是厲害啊 小理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經熟悉這裡的球道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是魚雷員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼刁鑽的角度都能命中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她輕鬆一拋就打中了 但正常是辦不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一個輪到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飛鏢我還是贏不過小光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來玩撞球吧 那邊還有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡沒有套圈圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還希望你能告訴我哪裡有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有投環的話 在陸地上還不如在船上有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也覺得在船上舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然累人 但是很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道晴風號能不能早點修好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能修好就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起來玩飛鏢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撞球也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼多人的話不應該打保齡球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不不 這時候就應該套圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 我還有任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是有機會的話肯定一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的話我想和全班同學一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全班的話也太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聚得起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的幫派會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒了要抬的神輿節日也該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是時候準備一下分別時的酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少我覺得應該不是什麼小事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或許這是最後一次讓大家聚在一起的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說 我們沒有船…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們班…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還…還沒定呢 先保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 我剛才收到一則訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道小依和小玉在什麼地方了 好像有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去把命令書交給小依和小玉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}航海科這之後會去溝板路的餐廳一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我去航海科那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完了 班級要解散了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家好不容易這麼熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後不能和大家一起上船了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們在閒聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們不是在打麻將嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留奈輸得額頭都被我彈痛了 想來玩別的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來大家感情都還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們聚在一起是在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣的 千萬別告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 用居飛車來舟圍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs華康儷中黑\fs25\1c&HECE6F2&\3c&H0F00E9&\frz352.4\pos(368,426)}貓咪也能看懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H1E233A&\fs30\frz353.1\pos(414,574)\frx20\fry350}將棋教學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡就是你的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這下小玉的船就四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的自主研修挺有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對吧 這樣手感就不會退化了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久沒有和麻侖兩個人一起做點什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶爾這樣也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}技術果然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你在這
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是明石號艦長杉本珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我聽說了奇怪的傳聞 跑來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有事要和你們說 有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還…沒定下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美波同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學校發的規定了啟封時間的密封命令書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回研究室了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}衣不解帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:42.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\1c&H625C9A&\be1\frx336\fry354\frz10.95\move(398,232,184,280,0,5504)}衣不解帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:42.04,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\1c&H6D7070&\be1\fs25\frx352\fry2\frz10.14\move(446,498,234,548,0,5504)}熱衷於某一件事情，連換衣服的工夫都沒有。指廢寢忘食地投身工作。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不換衣服 廢寢忘食地投身工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 現在是一口氣拉開戰線的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}星星之火 一下子就能燒遍整個棋盤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你們這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說我們會被拆散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先冷靜點 上面還沒有給出正式通知
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是剛才我們在和式甜點屋看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}間宮號的艦長在遊說小橘還有杵崎姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說明石號艦長也邀請了小侖和小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比叡號之類的地方肯定會來挖我們的航海長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要啊 我才不要和晴風號的大家分開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我眼裡的艦長只有岬同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來這是調動命令書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妳這麼晚還沒回來 我就先開始觀賞電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們班…可能要被解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傳聞原來是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家會被拆散…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的家要沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萬一真變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要來我們學校留學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:25.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,495)\rnd10}多災多難的納沙幸子
Comment: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:25.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:31.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:37.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:43.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:23:00.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:07.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:13.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:30.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:38.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:44.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:48.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:53.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:31.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:37.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我會比話語還要溫柔 輕輕地推著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:43.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是啊 這就是你和我之間的漣漪效應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:23:00.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}面前的驚濤駭浪 一浪捲來一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:07.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}我們選擇的航路 就是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:13.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}如果你忘記了微笑 我會笑給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:21.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}流過眼淚之後 讓堅強隨波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:30.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}比話語還要溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:38.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}是這片晴空和習習涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:44.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描繪夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:48.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}我希望我就是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:53.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}要相信春天正在等待著我們
